{"id":27585,"date":"2024-02-22T18:12:00","date_gmt":"2024-02-22T12:42:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=27585"},"modified":"2024-04-17T14:56:43","modified_gmt":"2024-04-17T09:26:43","slug":"karthigai-deepam-decoration-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/karthigai-deepam-decoration-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"Celebrate Karthigai Deepam With Diya Decoration Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Celebrated on the auspicious full moon day in the month of Kartika, Karthigai Deepam signifies the supremacy of Lord Shiva. Popularly known for its festival lights in the southern part of India, this is the day when Tamilians worldwide light up their homes with beautiful lamps, flowers and kolam. While oil lamps or diya are an essential part of most Hindu festivals, it is an indispensable part of Karthigai Deepam. It is a widespread belief that these festive lights protect the house from evil energy and bring immense joy and prosperity.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Karthigai Deepam also resembles the festivals of Bhai Dooj and Raksha Bandhan as it celebrates the beautiful bond between brothers and sisters. At this time of the year, sisters keep fast all day and pray for their brother\u2019s long life and well-being by lighting diyas. This is the time when the entire state comes together to celebrate the festival of lights. Tamil Nadu twinkles with oil lamps lit in all houses to spread the warmth of Indian culture and traditions and push away all darkness and negative energy from life while embracing the divine vibe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With that being said, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">DesignCafe<\/a> brings you some simple yet breathtaking Karthigai Diya decoration ideas for your home that will lend the spiritual vibe this festival deserves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Kolam Wallpaper, Oil Lamps And Fairy Lights To Celebrate Karthigai Deepam The Authentic Way<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Kolam is considered very auspicious in any Tamil household. The floral patterned painting on the floor with rice flour paste is believed to bring positivity to the space and keep evil energies at bay. In addition to making an intricate kolam at the entryway, you can also use it to accentuate your living room walls. A Kolam wall sticker like the one shown in the image can take your traditional festive home decor to a whole new level. You can also add some fresh flower garlands, oil lamps, and hanging lamps to add to the spirit of this festival of lights.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130618\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-kolam-oil-lamp.jpg\" alt=\"Karthigai deepam decoration with kolam wallpaper and oil lamps\" class=\"wp-image-51951\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130618\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-kolam-oil-lamp.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130618\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-kolam-oil-lamp-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130618\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-kolam-oil-lamp-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130618\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-kolam-oil-lamp-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A kolam wallpaper for Karthigai Deepam decorations<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Decorate Wooden Furniture With Festive Lights To Rejuvenate The Festive Spirit<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to decorate your home in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/traditional-interior-design-ideas\/\">traditional interior design<\/a> without giving up on the recent trends? Well, we have blended vintage and modern elements perfectly for you to strike the correct balance. The wooden sofa unit with cushioned seats and traditional wooden coffee table infuses a vintage vibe. At the same time, the intricate wall pieces and royal lighting wall sconces ring in some trends. You can add a traditional swing and decorate it with marigold garlands for additional seating options. This piece of furniture will elevate the design by several notches. Place some clay and floating lamps on the coffee table and around the corners to illuminate the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130535\/karthigai-deepam-decor-for-wooden-furniture.jpg\" alt=\"Karthigai Deepam decoration with festive lights on wooden furniture\" class=\"wp-image-51946\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130535\/karthigai-deepam-decor-for-wooden-furniture.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130535\/karthigai-deepam-decor-for-wooden-furniture-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130535\/karthigai-deepam-decor-for-wooden-furniture-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130535\/karthigai-deepam-decor-for-wooden-furniture-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Living room with floral decorations &amp; festive lights<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">DIY Diya Decoration Ideas To Embrace The Karthigai Festival<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Festivals are a great way to teach our traditions and culture to our little ones. While they might be least interested in cleaning, you can involve them in preparing some creative DIY festive decor items. Craft and create diya-shaped paper cuttings and origami hangers with your kids and attach them to the fairy lights. These lighting arrangements will add a new dimension to your Karthigai Deepam decoration whilst keeping your kids busy with creative activities as you finish off your festive preparations and help them develop an interest in Indian culture and traditions.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130609\/diy-karthigai-deepam-decor.jpg\" alt=\"DIY Karthigai deepam decor to embrace the festivities\" class=\"wp-image-51950\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130609\/diy-karthigai-deepam-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130609\/diy-karthigai-deepam-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130609\/diy-karthigai-deepam-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130609\/diy-karthigai-deepam-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Celebration of lights this Karthigai Festival with DIY decor activities<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Use Mango Leaves, Oil Lamps And Flowers To Decorate Your Pooja Room For Karthigai Light Festival<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mango leaves, fresh flowers, and oil lamps are key ingredients for this Karthigai Deepam festival at home. And you can incorporate these elements to create a simple yet elegant decorated pooja space in your home. Clean up your pooja room, use some mango leaf toran and fresh flowers to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/how-to-choose-entryway-rugs\/\">decorate the entrance<\/a> of your pooja room. Fresh flowers and mango leaves will infuse a sweet fragrance in your entire room and create a festive mood. Make a small floral rangoli at the entrance and place diyas and oil lamps around it. You can also place two hanging brass hanging diyas to accentuate the beauty of the space. Hang some Thanjavur paintings on your living room wall to lend a temple theme to your space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130601\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-mango-leaves.jpg\" alt=\"Karthigai deepam decoration with mango leaves and flowers\" class=\"wp-image-51949\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130601\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-mango-leaves.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130601\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-mango-leaves-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130601\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-mango-leaves-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130601\/karthigai-deepam-decor-with-mango-leaves-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Karthigai Light Festival decoration ideas for your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Decorated Entryway To Bring In Prosperity And Happiness To Your Home On Tamil Karthigai Deepam<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A decorated entryway creates the perfect mood for the entire home. This Karthigai Deepam, you can make a kolam in front of the door or a floral rangoli and decorate it with oil lamps. Place a brass bowl filled with water and floating lamps beside the kolam. Decorate the top of your foyer unit with flowers, small decor items, and candle stands to jazz up the space. Hang some light strings and flowers to stitch the look together.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130552\/entryway-karthigai-deepam-decor.jpg\" alt=\"Karthigai deepam decor of your entryway to bring prosperity\" class=\"wp-image-51948\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130552\/entryway-karthigai-deepam-decor.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130552\/entryway-karthigai-deepam-decor-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130552\/entryway-karthigai-deepam-decor-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130552\/entryway-karthigai-deepam-decor-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Decorate the entryway for a grand Tamil Karthigai Deepam<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Simple Karthigai Deepam Decorations For A Subtle Festive Touch To Your Modern Interiors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Too busy to celebrate the festival with great pomp and show, yet want to bring in a subtle festive vibe of Karthigai Deepam in your home? Well, we have a perfect hack to infuse a subtle traditional vibe into your ultra-modern home. Decorate your space-saving entertainment unit with some fresh flower garlands. Optionally, you can also add a festival-themed wallpaper for a quick makeover. Placing some diyas around the low-lying cabinet with drawers and some around the fairy lights will do the trick.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130544\/simple-karthigai-deepam-decoration.jpg\" alt=\"Karthigai deepam decoration with a subtle festive touch\" class=\"wp-image-51947\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130544\/simple-karthigai-deepam-decoration.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130544\/simple-karthigai-deepam-decoration-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130544\/simple-karthigai-deepam-decoration-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/24130544\/simple-karthigai-deepam-decoration-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Simple Karthigai Deepam decoration for your home<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We hope you enjoyed our Karthigai Deepam home decoration ideas as much as we enjoyed curating them for you. If you want to revamp your home or get your home interiors done by expert designers, then you can connect with our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/cities\/interior-designers-chennai\/\">top designers in Chennai <\/a>and get started on the home interiors of your dreams! Book an appointment today and leave the rest to us.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Here\u2019s wishing you and your family a happy and prosperous Karthigai Deepam!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">FAQs On Karthigai Deepam Decor<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are the traditional decorations for Karthigai Deepam?<\/strong><br>Traditional decorations for Karthigai Deepam include lighting oil lamps, displaying clay lamps, and decorating with fresh flowers and rangoli.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are some popular Karthigai Deepam kolam designs?<\/strong><br>Popular Karthigai Deepam kolam designs feature intricate patterns of lamps, flowers, and traditional symbols, often drawn in vibrant colours to mark the occasion.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What are some flower decoration ideas for Karthigai Deepam?<\/strong><br>Flower decoration ideas for Karthigai Deepam involve creating vibrant rangoli designs with flower petals, using marigold garlands, and adorning entrances with fragrant jasmine strings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>How can I make my Karthigai Deepam decorations eco-friendly?<\/strong><br>To make Karthigai Deepam decorations eco-friendly, opt for clay lamps instead of plastic, use organic materials for rangoli, and choose natural, biodegradable decorations like fresh flowers and banana leaves.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\